               <p>Incomplete set of a printed newsletter published in Paris, containing news of the AFFW, and donations desired. Issues list officers, staff, and American chapters. The June 1916 issue contains the article, "A Visit to Dr. Carrel's Hospital."</p>
            </scopecontent>
