            <scopecontent id="aspace_e82f9969b2e1a7797c336b65b9f1fc2b">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Eight postcards. Only one relates directly to AFFW, an image of the birthplace of Marechal Joffre in 1917 showing an AFFW car distributing supplies. Five cards have handwritten notes in French. Three show hospitals or hospital staff. See also postcard in Folder 1.</p>
